        <p>Yotpo Email & SMS vs Drip: scenario 1 — BNPL selected then dropped at review. At $312 AOV and 71% margin, full-price recovery contributes $221.52 vs $179.43 after a 19% code (Δ $42.09). Ladder touch 1 favors push nudge; watch for duplicate SMS and email within 20 minutes. Email 1 ~93m, email 2 ~46h, SMS branch ~5h for opted-in only.</p>
